                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tech-activity-card">
                <div class="activity-icon mobile">
                    <i class="bi bi-phone"></i>
                </div>
                <h4>Mobile Development</h4>
                <p>
                    Experience building native Android apps with Kotlin/Java and iOS apps with Swift, 
                    plus cross-platform development with React Native.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="tech-activity-card">
                <div class="activity-icon iot">
                    <i class="bi bi-hdd-network"></i>
                </div>
